org.sql: SELECT users.id, users_settings.feed_url FROM users INNER JOIN users_settings ON users_settings.user_id = users.id WHERE users.id IN (SELECT users_settings.user_id FROM users_settings WHERE users_settings.feed_url IS NULL) AND users.id = "$1"

rewrites.sql: SELECT users.id, users_settings.feed_url FROM users INNER JOIN users_settings ON users_settings.user_id = users.id WHERE users.id IN (SELECT users_settings.user_id FROM users_settings WHERE users_settings.feed_url IS NULL) AND users.id = "$1" LIMIT 1
